Package ezvcard.parameters

Class Summary
AddressTypeParameter Represents the TYPE parameter of the AddressType and LabelType types.
CalscaleParameter Represents a CALSCALE parameter.
EmailTypeParameter Represents the TYPE parameter of the EmailType type.
EncodingParameter Represents the "ENCODING" sub type.
ExpertiseLevelParameter Represents a LEVEL parameter for the ExpertiseType property.
HobbyLevelParameter Represents a LEVEL parameter for the HobbyType property.
ImageTypeParameter Represents an image media type used in the TYPE parameter, MEDIATYPE parameter, and data URIs of the PhotoType and LogoType properties.
ImppTypeParameter Represents the TYPE parameter of the ImppType type.
InterestLevelParameter Represents a LEVEL parameter for the InterestType property.
KeyTypeParameter Represents the TYPE parameter of the KeyType type.
MediaTypeCaseClasses<T extends MediaTypeParameter> Manages the list of pre-defined values for a media type parameter.
MediaTypeParameter Represents a TYPE parameter that also has a media type associated with it.
RelatedTypeParameter Represents the TYPE parameter of the RelatedType type.
SoundTypeParameter Represents the TYPE parameter of the SoundType type.
TelephoneTypeParameter Represents the TYPE parameter of the TelephoneType type.
VCardParameter Represents a vCard parameter (aka "sub type") whose values are pre-defined.
VCardParameterCaseClasses<T extends VCardParameter> Manages the list of pre-defined values for a parameter that consists of a single String value.
VersionedVCardParameter Represents a parameter whose values are supported by a variety of different vCard versions.
